descript.abstract: This is a polygon theme indicating the extent of fires for 2003 - 2004 fire year within the Kruger National Park (KNP). The KNP falls under the authority of South African National Parks (www.parks-sa.co.za).
descript.purpose: Burn blocks data have been captured and processed for cartographic production and spatial analysis by scientists undertaking research in the Kruger National Park.
descript.supplinf: It is our intention to maintain roads in our database which have fallen into disuse. These are important for historical analysis as they formed boundaries to burn-blocks, ranger sections and other regional divisions.
